snippet.title: Afloat - gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Afloat is a VR survial game where you can build, craft and survive in the jungle on a small raft. 

Afloat is now available on itch.io and will be coming to steam early acces this summer

Discord: https://discord.gg/exCSMCq
